{"type": "article", "id": 26098, "title": "便携式蓝牙扬声器", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-28T07:10:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145808EqG4cgOpQPuh0SfC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.beoplay.com/\">BeoPlay A1</a> 是丹麦品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen 最新推出的一款蓝牙扬声器，小巧精致的造型强调出的是便携性，对于大大小小的派对场合来说非常实用。铝合金外壳表面的触感光滑，没有设计凸起的操纵按钮，总重量约为 590 克。你还可以下载一个 <a href=\"http://www.beoplay.com/products/beoplayapp#pairing\" onclick=\"recordOutboundLink(this, 'Linkout', 'http://www.beoplay.com/products/beoplayapp#pairing'); return true;\" target=\"_blank\">BeoPlay app</a> 来控制它播放音乐，很有科技感。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145804PaVU2nRCFGDwz7NZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145806yei4HsXgbOtK7V1Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145807kG2uyX5DH1l8QARq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145808KBuZd0RUYjglocbF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}